{
  "texts": [
    "The increasing popularity of interaction in iVR experiences was reflected in the growing use of Interactive experiences (78.6%).",
    "In addition, this type of experience can be performed with Desktop 6DOF devices.",
    "In contrast, Explorative experiences were less common (8.2%) and they commonly used Standalone and Desktop 6DOF HMDs.",
    "Those devices enable the user to move through the virtual environment using controllers, which can involve natural movements and even their own physiological parameters.",
    "Desktop 6DOF HMDs were the only HMDs used for Explorative with interaction experiences (8.2%)."
  ]
}